title: I’m Not That Kind of Talent
summary: I’m Not That Kind of Talent Manhwa I’m not that kind of person. I, Dion Hart, am a sickly person who vomits blood whenever I’m stressed. However, at the same time, I’m Count Hart, who has somehow been misunderstood and thought of as a strong person, and thereby feared by everyone. 저 그런 인재 아닙니다
